- Test (full): TEST_ALL_COMMAND
- Lint/format: LINT_COMMAND
- Typecheck: TYPECHECK_COMMAND

## Boundaries

Always:
- Run TYPECHECK_COMMAND and relevant tests after a series of changes
- Follow existing patterns; EXAMPLE_FILE is a good reference

Ask first:
- Database schema or migration changes
- Adding new dependencies
- ANYTHING_ELSE_RISKY

Never:
- Commit secrets or .env files
- Edit VENDOR_OR_GENERATED_DIRS
- Push directly to MAIN_BRANCH

## Knowledge

- Before architectural changes: check docs/decisions/
- Before working in DOMAIN_X: read docs/gotchas/DOMAIN_X.md
- Non-trivial work: /research then /plan before implementing
- Made a mistake this session? Run /learn before finishing. Made a judgment call? /log-decision.

